apihelp-wikispeech-param-removetags:
The tags that should be removed completely during cleaning, as a JSON object of the format:
<pre>{
  "tagName1": true,
  "tagName2": "cssClass"
}</pre>
where <code>tagName1</code> is always removed and <code>tagName2</code> is only removed if it also has the CSS class <code>cssClass</code>.
